  "title": "Cobblemon: Additions & Tools",
  "description": "Adds 7 armor and 40+ special tools made from evolution stones.",
  "body": "<h1><span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong>Cobblemon: Additions</strong></span></h1>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">◽ The project aims to add various items, armor, ores, tools and weapons based on the cobblemon mod.</span></strong><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">If you want to play this version of the mod with the recipes from MOD CREATE, visit the link to my other mod :</span></strong> <span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong><a title=\"Create: Cobblemon Industries\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-create-industries\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Create: Cobblemon Industries</a></strong></span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong>Current Features:</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">◽ </span>Armor<br>- Adds 8 new armors, better than diamond ones, with enchantments and permanent potion effects.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong>◽ Tools and weapons.<br>- Added 40 new tools and weapons with enchantments when crafting.</strong></span></p>\n<hr>\n<h1>Armor's</h1>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\"><strong>Armor Type</strong></th>\n<th style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\"><strong>Special Effect</strong></th>\n<th style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\"><strong>Boots Enchantment</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Fire Stone</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Fire Resistance</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Fire Protection II</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Water Stone</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Water Breathing</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Aqua Affinity II</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Leaf Stone</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">N/A</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Feather Falling III + Thorns III</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Thunder Stone</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Haste II + 50% Movement Speed</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">N/A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Sun Stone</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">N/A</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Protection IV + Projectile Protection IV</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Moon Stone</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">N/A</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Protection IV + Blast Protection IV</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Dawn Stone</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Jump Boost IV + Fall Damage Immunity</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">N/A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Dusk Stone</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">Saturation</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid #ccc;\">N/A</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>- All armors are made with their respective evolutionary stone.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_6a264b91-140c-42d4-bebf-f461fedf6632.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"345\" height=\"215\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_f5348add-f280-4475-80be-e313b4c314fb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"340\" height=\"215\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_a1ac8df3-d51c-470a-9603-b0f23174a1f8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"155\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_042b6cd6-ada2-48a3-8b4c-b7ac0781f984.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"824\" height=\"170\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_2c42bba3-6a8c-4df0-a10b-4a8102c8ab98.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"130\" height=\"202\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_66510804-6e5b-43fe-9b02-0214d9863f95.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"125\" height=\"201\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_d088154b-d0ae-45c1-bba0-5c352a910210.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"129\" height=\"202\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_02701298-5f6e-4511-a3f4-1a776027c12b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"129\" height=\"200\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_5862ee7b-c5d6-4dd7-bdaa-0e267f4d4231.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"116\" height=\"201\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_31ed17b0-0cb5-4b01-b258-76a59aaadc9e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"122\" height=\"202\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_60f3bb04-6f98-4b40-8276-795cc2ec4509.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"124\" height=\"223\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_d7caa27c-a9ea-4004-8d7a-e26c2fd16d7e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"127\" height=\"208\"></p>",
